<div id="coworkspace" class="">
  <h1>COWORKSPACE</h1>
  <div class="coworkspace-details ml-0">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between row mt-1 mb-4 align-items-center coworkspace-intro">
      <%= image_tag "all_coworkspace.svg", class: "coworkspace_images col-12 col-lg-8", width: 700 %>
      <p class="description-coworkspace col-12 col-lg-4">
        The Coworkspace project was elected and coded as a team during the last two weeks of <a href="https://www.lewagon.com/fr" target="_blank" class="link-red">Le Wagon</a>.
        <br>
        <br>
        The project was presented during the demoday, the last day of the 9 weeks of the Bootcamp.
        <br>
        <br>
        <span>
          <a href="https://coworkspace-paulinedussart.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank" class="link-red"><i class="fas fa-globe mr-2"></i>Coworkspace</a> <br>
          <a href="https://github.com/paulinedussart/coworkspace" target="_blank" class="link-red"><i class="fab fa-github-alt mr-2"></i>Github project</a>
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="developed-features little-text-space mt-5">Main Features Developed</h3>
    <ul class="ml-4">
      <li>A simplified reservation system</li>
      <li>Online direct payment with Stripe</li>
      <li>Booking history for users and the coworking space.</li>
      <li>A dashboard for coworkspace manager </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
      <div class="justify-content-end mt-5 little-text-space">
        <h3>Roles</h3>
        <p>Everybody in the group worked on back and front developpement. I mainly take care about the design of the home page, the paiement process, the result page and the description of the coworkspace.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide p-4" data-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators" style="bottom: -25px">
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_find.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_book.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_paiement.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_reservations.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>


    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-5">
      <div class=" little-text-space toto ">
        <h3>Mains Difficulties</h3>
        <h5 class="ml-3">Organizational </h5>
        <p class="ml-5">We used Trello to organize the work between the team members. For this kind of project, the communication with the team is very important about the progress.</p>
        <h5 class="ml-3">Technical</h5>
        <p class="ml-5"> The main difficulty was to organize work between the skills of eachother. Be focus on the user case presented the evening of the demonstration day. </p>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class=" mt-5 d-flex justify-content-end mb-5">
      <div class="little-text-space">
        <h3>Skills and knowledge developed</h3>
        <p>I was lucky that my project was selected. So I could see the creation from it's idea to it's development and presentation.
          Today I am able to have a global vision of a product. From its database to it's development and production. </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide p-4" data-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators" style="bottom: -25px">
        <li data-target="#carouselExample" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExample" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExample" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExample" data-slide-to="3"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_find.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_book.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_paiement.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <%= image_tag "coworkspace_reservations.svg", class: "d-block w-100" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExample" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon mr-4" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExample" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon ml-4" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mb-3">
      <a href="https://coworkspace-paulinedussart.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank" class="link-red"> Coworkspace</a> <br>
      <a href="https://github.com/paulinedussart/coworkspace" target="_blank" class="link-red"><i class="fab fa-github-alt mr-2"></i>Github project</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>